<br>
Do I need a key to get into Skyshrine from Wakening Lands side?<br>
<br>
What's a good spot for a 45 Troll Warrior and 45 Human Cleric to hunt in Wakening Land? Were on CoV, for safety reasons, and Coldain faction currently. KOS to Giants. Could we do Suits of Sentient Armor?<br>
<br>
Thanks for your input.<br>
<br>
 <p>Tunnel Rat X
<BR>
