</A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ulivtinth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Livtinth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Guru</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/31/02 1:19:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1660.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Two Questions...ok maybe a few...</span><hr size=1> guess so.<br>
<br>
no.<br>
<br>
you could try. but they have a ton of hp and hit quite hard unslowed. (read: there are way better places than WL) <p><center><img src=http://www.legacyofsteel.net/images/screenshots/december_01/12_30/allakhazam.jpg><br><small><font color=gray><b><a href=http://www.legacyofsteel.net>http://www.legacyofsteel.net</a></small></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/upalimaxsceleris.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Palimax Sceleris</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Local Resident</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/31/02 4:58:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1660.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Two Questions...ok maybe a few...</span><hr size=1> Charged items can be recharged at the vendor, but not in the way you describe.<br>
<br>
Since it's one of those &quot;not so legal&quot; things, I'll leave out the details. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4868>Palimax Sceleris</a>,
Guildleader: <a href=http://www.guildvision.org>Vision</a>, Grandmaster <a href=http://www.base-nine.org/available_tinkering_items.htm>Tinkerer</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uicklymuk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Icklymuk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Boardfellow</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/31/02 5:08:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1660.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Two Questions...ok maybe a few...</span><hr size=1> Re-charging items...<br>
<br>
Re-charging items only works if the item stacks and you have one item that isn't out of charges...<br>
<br>
<br>
For the leather foot raider cap, sorry I'm pretty sure that it wouldn't work...<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/unluien.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nluien</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Veteran</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/31/02 5:41:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1660.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Two Questions...ok maybe a few...</span><hr size=1> You do not need a key to get from Wakening Lands into Skyshrine.  You do need a key to get from Skyshrine to Cobalt Scars though.<br>
<br>
And the sentient suits, like said above, are very difficult if not slowed or fear kited.  So I dont think the two of you could kill them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/upalimaxsceleris.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Palimax Sceleris</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Post-o-holic</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/31/02 7:00:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1660.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Two Questions...ok maybe a few...</span><hr size=1> ...the items don't have to be stackable.<br>
<br>
Rallos people, for example, recharge Ivandyr's Hoops and Wands of Conflag all the time. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4868>Palimax Sceleris</a>,
Guildleader: <a href=http://www.guildvision.org>Vision</a>, Grandmaster <a href=http://www.base-nine.org/available_tinkering_items.htm>Tinkerer</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/utunnelratx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TunnelRatX</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Veteran</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/31/02 7:39:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1660.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.fearlessblack.net/images/Maulo003.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Two Questions...ok maybe a few...</span><hr size=1> Anything else I can kill in Wakening Land then with a 45 War and 45 Cleric?<br>
 <p>Tunnel Rat X
